videoDetails.Title: Making a Game With A Graphic Calculator Desmos
videoDetails.Description:
In this video, we will create a simple obstacle-avoidance game, inside a Graphical Calculator "Desmos".

Reid Captain's Series: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL2lqjYK9wCjzC4Y9xHYhot8YCXMpe9s35
